'''Gree spice''' was a purple form of [[Spice/Legends|spice]]. It granted the user a sense of happiness and power. This [[Spice/Legends|spice]] was not encouraged by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]], but was legal. The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], however, made it illegal.

